title: Art Institute of Chicago Watercolor Paint Set
description:
Paint set developed with our current logo, designed in 2008 by Abbott Miller, partner of Pentagram.

A compact water color set for you to create with, or give as a gift to a friend.  There are three stacked trays with six unique colors each or eighteen colors total.   A fun portable set of watercolors.

  • Dimensions of each tray:  3.25 in. in diameter.
  • Number of trays:  3
  • Colors: 6 per tray, 18 different colors total.
